Interface FunctionalI<T,R>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BooleanSupplier, Consumer<T>, DoubleConsumer, DoubleFunction<R>, DoublePredicate, DoubleSupplier, DoubleToIntFunction, DoubleToLongFunction, DoubleUnaryOperator, Function<T,R>, IntConsumer, IntFunction<R>, IntPredicate, IntSupplier, IntToDoubleFunction, IntToLongFunction, IntUnaryOperator, LongConsumer, LongFunction<R>, LongPredicate, LongSupplier, LongToDoubleFunction, LongToIntFunction, LongUnaryOperator, Predicate<T>, Supplier<R>, ToDoubleFunction<T>, ToIntFunction<T>, ToLongFunction<T>
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface FunctionalI<T,R>
extends Function<T,R>, Predicate<T>, Consumer<T>, Supplier<R>, IntUnaryOperator, LongUnaryOperator, DoubleUnaryOperator, IntFunction<R>, LongFunction<R>, DoubleFunction<R>, ToIntFunction<T>, ToLongFunction<T>, ToDoubleFunction<T>, IntToLongFunction, IntToDoubleFunction, LongToIntFunction, LongToDoubleFunction, DoubleToIntFunction, DoubleToLongFunction, IntPredicate, LongPredicate, DoublePredicate, IntConsumer, LongConsumer, DoubleConsumer, IntSupplier, LongSupplier, DoubleSupplier, BooleanSupplier
